OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FITV News has found that since 2016 the
OL,8,FCQC, the independent regulator of
OL,9,Fhealth and social care in England, has
OL,10,Fprosecuted just 11 providers relating
OL,11,Fto the care of people with learning
OL,12,Fdisabilities - Investigations Editor
OL,13,FDaniel Hewitt has more
OL,15,FCare companies who look after people
OL,16,Fwith learning disabilities are not
OL,17,Fbeing inspected often enough, the Care
OL,18,FQuality Commission has admitted to ITV
OL,19,FNews, as families say the health
OL,20,Fregulator is failing to prosecute
OL,21,Fproviders of negligent care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FIn an exclusive interview, the CQC's
OL,8,FChief Inspector of Adult Social care
OL,9,Fsaid he would make increasing
OL,10,Finspections his "number one priority"
OL,11,Fand would personally prioritise the
OL,12,Fcare of people with learning
OL,13,Fdisabilities and autism, following an
OL,14,FITV News investigation which has found
OL,15,Fmultiple failings across the sector.
OL,26,@rD@QOUrD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe CQC, which regulates health and
OL,8,Fsocial care settings in England, has
OL,9,Fthe power to prosecute care providers
OL,10,Ffor "severe or persistent breaches of
OL,11,Fsafety", but ITV news has found that
OL,12,Fsince 2016 the regular has prosecuted
OL,13,Fjust 11 providers relating to the care
OL,14,Fof people with learning disabilities.
OL,26,@rD@EOUsD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThat's despite ITV News speaking to
OL,8,Fhundreds of families since February
OL,9,F2025 alleging negligent care of their
OL,10,Frelatives with learning disabilities,
OL,11,Fincluding 9 men and women who have
OL,12,Fdied while under the care of providers
OL,13,Fregulated by the CQC. In none of those
OL,14,Fcases were any of the care providers
OL,15,Fprosecuted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThose nine cases include a man with
OL,8,FDown Syndrome who was starved to death
OL,9,Fin an NHS hospital, a young man who
OL,10,Fwas given the wrong blood-thinning
OL,11,Fmedication because doctor's wrongly
OL,12,Fdidn't believe he was taking it, and a
OL,13,Fman who choked to death on a sandwich
OL,14,Fbecause carers left him unattended in
OL,15,Fa private care home.
OL,17,FThe CQC's Chief Inspector admitted the
OL,18,Fregulator needs to inspect the quality
OL,19,Fof care "more consistently and more
OL,20,Fregularly" than it has been doing.
OL,26,@{D@IOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"My number one priority as Chief
OL,8,FInspector is to do more inspections
OL,9,Fand get out and see more services,"
OL,10,Fsaid Chris Badger, who was appointed
OL,11,Fin September 2025.
OL,13,F"We have done 68% more inspections
OL,14,Fthis year than last year, but we need
OL,15,Fto go further. When we do that and we
OL,16,Fdo more assessments, it's likely that
OL,17,Fwe'll have more enforcement action all
OL,18,Fthe way through from warning notices,
OL,19,Fpotentially prosecutions.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@cO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"The care of people with learning
OL,8,Fdisabilities and autism is a really
OL,9,Fsignificant priority for me
OL,10,Fpersonally."
OL,12,FFamilies have told ITV News they
OL,13,Fbelieve the CQC is denying them
OL,14,Fjustice through a lack of action.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/27
