OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FSally Lewis had a learning disability
OL,8,Fand lived in a care home in Worcester
OL,9,Frun by Dimensions. In October 2017 her
OL,10,Fsister Julie Bennett received a phone
OL,11,Fcall to say Sally had died suddenly,
OL,12,Fwith no explanation, and no prior
OL,13,Fwarning that she was unwell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe postmortem report found Sally had
OL,8,Fdied from constipation. Dimensions
OL,9,Fclaimed that there had been no
OL,10,Fdisceprancies with Sally's medication,
OL,11,Fbut it was discovered that for 300
OL,12,Fdays carers had failed to give her
OL,13,Fregular prescribed laxative medication
OL,14,Fas stated in her care plan.
OL,16,FSally, who was almost entirely non-
OL,17,Fverbal, was unable to say anything.
OL,19,FAn inquest later found Sally had died
OL,20,Ffrom neglect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"I phoned the CQC, because they
OL,8,F(Dimensions) should be held
OL,9,Faccountable for killing my sister,"
OL,10,Fsaid Julie.
OL,12,F"They asked me what had happened to my
OL,13,Fsister. I said she died and (they)
OL,14,Fsaid I'll take your details someone
OL,15,Fwill ring you back. No phone call
OL,16,Fback, nothing.
OL,18,F"I just presumed that they were
OL,19,Flooking into it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@cO]tD@AOUzD@AOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FIt took the CQC a further three years
OL,8,Fto bring a criminal case against
OL,9,FDimensions for Sally's death, by which
OL,10,Fpoint it was too late. A judge threw
OL,11,Fthe case out because it went beyond
OL,12,Fthe statutory three-year time limit.
OL,14,F"It's disgraceful, disgraceful," Julie
OL,15,Ftold ITV News.
OL,17,F"They are there to make sure providers
OL,18,Foffer a safe, effective environment -
OL,19,Fit says that on their website. And
OL,20,Fthey did nothing."
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@`O]yD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe CQC has apologised for failing to
OL,8,Fhold anyone to account to Sally's
OL,9,Fdeath.
OL,11,F"It is important to say I'm really
OL,12,Fsorry that we weren't able to take
OL,13,Fforward that prosecution," said Chris
OL,14,FBadger.
OL,16,F"At the time I know the CQC were keen
OL,17,Fto do that, and the issue of the
OL,18,Fstatute to limitations or the time
OL,19,Ftaken meant that that wasn't able to
OL,20,Fproceed."
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@ZO]xD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FIn a statement, the chief executive of
OL,8,FDimensions Rachael Dodgson said:
OL,10,F"Sally Lewis's death nine years ago
OL,11,Fremains a source of deep sadness for
OL,12,Fall of us in Dimensions. We accepted
OL,13,Fthe Coroner's conclusion that Sally's
OL,14,Fpreventable death was contributed to
OL,15,Fby neglect. Our care in relation to
OL,16,FSally's bowel health fell far short of
OL,17,Four standards. We are truly sorry.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"Sally's family quite rightly expect
OL,8,Ffull accountability. Sally's death
OL,9,Fprofoundly changed our organisation.
OL,10,FFollowing Sally's death in 2017 we
OL,11,Fmade immediate improvements in both
OL,12,Fhow we support people at risk of
OL,13,Fconstipation, and our management
OL,14,Foversight of that risk."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31815
