CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe relatives of people with learning
OL,8,Fdisabilities have consistently told
OL,9,FITV News that the CQC is slow to
OL,10,Frespond to their complaints, sometimes
OL,11,Fnot replying at all, with some care
OL,12,Fhomes not inspected for more than five
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FJoanna Crook has complained multiple
OL,16,Ftimes to the CQC with serious concerns
OL,17,Fabout the welfare of her son.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FAdam is 36 years old and has Down
OL,8,Fsyndrome, autism and is non-verbal. He
OL,9,Frequires full-time, specialist care
OL,10,Fwhich he is meant to receive at
OL,11,FVoyage, a private care company owned
OL,12,Fby Kuwait and its sovereign wealth
OL,13,Ffund.
OL,15,FSince 2021, Joanna says Adam has
OL,16,Fdeclined under Voyage due to
OL,17,F"appalling care".
OL,19,F"He never smiles anymore," she tells
OL,20,Fme. "He lives an impoverished life."
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@PO]{D@AOU{D@ZO]|D@EOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FIncidents Joanna has raised with the
OL,8,FCQC include an alleged assault by a
OL,9,FVoyage care worker, in public, in 2022
OL,10,Fand Adam appearing with severe
OL,11,Fchemical burns on his body in 2025.
OL,13,F"Somebody had witnessed a carer who
OL,14,Fhad Adam strapped in a wheelchair,
OL,15,Fslapping him around his head in the
OL,16,FCivic Centre," said Joanna.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"I sent a very emotional email to them
OL,8,F(the CQC) saying about all the
OL,9,Fsafeguarding and what are they going
OL,10,Fto do about it. I didn't get a reply
OL,11,Fto that.
OL,13,F"I met with Adam with carers for his
OL,14,Flearning disability review at the GP,
OL,15,Fand he was dirty, he had a swelling on
OL,16,Fthe side of his face, he actually had
OL,17,Fhis shoes on the wrong feet.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31819
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"I popped in there (to Voyage) and a
OL,8,Fstaff member had bought Adam out with
OL,9,Fthese burns on his buttocks. They were
OL,10,Fchemical burns, second degree burns,
OL,11,Fincredibly painful.
OL,13,F"He probably had those for 24 hours
OL,14,Fand he couldn't tell anyone. They had
OL,15,Fno first aid.
OL,17,F"The staff doing the one-to-one care
OL,18,Ffor 15 hours a day, every toilet,
OL,19,Fevery washing of hands, every change
OL,20,Fof clothes - the staff remained mute."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU|D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31820
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FAfter each incident Joanna contacted
OL,8,Fthe CQC, along with other concerns,
OL,9,Fwhose investigations into Adam's care
OL,10,Fprovider have never led to any
OL,11,Fpunishment or sanction against them.
OL,13,FAmlan Basu, Chief Operating Officer at
OL,14,FVoyage Care, said:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
