OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"The issues raised in this interview
OL,8,Fhave been thoroughly investigated and
OL,9,Fcarefully managed. We are deeply
OL,10,Fdisappointed that our high standards
OL,11,Fwere not met, and we have apologised
OL,12,Funreservedly to Adam and his mother.
OL,13,FWe remain committed to working with
OL,14,Fthem to address any concerns and
OL,15,Fensure they receive the right support".
OL,17,FThe Voyage care home Adam is living
OL,18,Fin, where the incidents took place, is
OL,19,Frated Good by the CQC, but it has not
OL,20,Fbeen inspected since April 2021.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/27
