CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"I know a little bit of background
OL,8,Fabout that case, clearly it is a live
OL,9,Fcase and I don't want to talk in
OL,10,Fdetail about what our next steps might
OL,11,Fbe," said Chris Badger.
OL,13,F"Five years (to inspect a care
OL,14,Fprovider) is longer than I would want.
OL,15,FI would like to get us to a position
OL,16,Fwhere we're inspecting care homes
OL,17,Fevery three years."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@DO]uD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
