OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31823
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FOn the accusation from multiple
OL,8,Ffamilies that the CQC either doesn't
OL,9,Frespond to their complaints or takes
OL,10,Flittle action when it does, the Chief
OL,11,FInspector insisted their numbers show
OL,12,Fa different story.
OL,14,F"We're responding to 95% (of
OL,15,Fcomplaints) within the day for what we
OL,16,Fcall the Priority One cases, where
OL,17,Fit's of the more serious level.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31824
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782427691
OL,3,CCQC admits disability care inspections
OL,4,Cmust improve after ITV News
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"We also work with local authorities
OL,8,Fand councils and also assessing care
OL,9,Fhomes, so I'm confident where we get
OL,10,Fthat information, we will look at that
OL,11,Finformation, deal with it really
OL,12,Fstrongly".
OL,14,FThat has not been the experience of
OL,15,FJulie and Joanna, who both feel the
OL,16,Fregulator has let them down when it
OL,17,Fcomes to keeping their loved ones safe
OL,18,Fand delivering justice when care goes
OL,19,Fwrong.
OL,26,@tD@IO]
